# Styling

- **Tailwind-first** — all styling via utility classes; no CSS modules or styled-components
- Global CSS is minimal (`src/app/globals.css`): body gradient, font smoothing, focus-visible, selection color, `.conf-fill`
- Custom theme tokens are defined in `tailwind.config.ts` — use semantic names not raw hex

## Color Palette

| Token | Use |
|-------|-----|
| `paper` / `paper-2` / `paper-3` | Backgrounds |
| `ink` / `ink-soft` | Primary text |
| `accent` / `accent-2` | CTAs, active states |
| `muted` / `muted-soft` | Secondary text |
| `brand-green` / `green-soft` | Success states |
| `card` / `card-hi` | Card backgrounds |

## Neo-Brutalist Shadows

Use `shadow-hard` for cards, `shadow-btn-accent` / `shadow-btn-ink` for buttons, `shadow-hard-sm` for small elements.

## Fonts

`font-serif` (Fraunces) for headings, `font-sans` (Inter Tight) for body, `font-mono` (JetBrains Mono) for code/data.
